<p>If you are finding best watch at age 24 and above then this watch is best for you. Diameter of this watch is 44 MM so it can easily fit on thick or medium wrist. With low price you are getting 24 months warranty instead of 12 month and also 50 M water resistant. So, you can use this watch in rain or at a time of hand washing.</p>
<p>This is such an amazing Titan’s Rounded watch. This is from one of the best branded and casual watches at a low budget. If you wear this kind of watch (I mean branded) the first time then you will fill yourself different from the community. If you wear your regular dress yet you get a nice look with this watch. A watch with a black leather belt and inside silver material gives a perfect match with a black shirt or T-shirt with blue jeans and white shoes. That is the perfect matching. It’s my own experience with this kind of titan watch.</p>
	
